summary: An ordinance authorizing the City Treasurer to accept Ninety ($90.00) Dollars in full satisfaction of a judgement in amount of One Hundred Thirty-four and 70/100 Dollars ($134.70) in the case of the City of Seattle, a municipal corporation, cs. H.B. Klinker, et ux., Cause No. 168761, and authorizing the Corporation Counsel to satisfy said judgement in full upon the payment of said sum of Ninety Dollars ($90.00) , and declaring an emergency.
